## Setup

```bash
# Install pixi if you haven't already: https://pixi.sh
pixi install

# Configure DVC remote (edit .dvc/config with your paths)
# Then: pixi run pull
```

## Usage

```bash
# Run the full DVC pipeline
pixi run pipeline

# Run a specific stage
dvc repro <stage_name>

# Run tests
pixi run test
{% if include_marimo %}
# Open a marimo notebook
pixi run -e notebooks notebook notebooks/marimo/explore.py
{% endif %}
```

## Project structure

```
├── {{ package_name }}/     # Importable analysis package (pip install -e .)
├── scripts/                # DVC pipeline stage scripts
├── data/                   # DVC-tracked data (per-session parquet files)
├── results/                # DVC-tracked outputs (figures, models)
├── conf/                   # Hydra / pipeline configuration
├── logs/                   # Per-stage log files
├── notebooks/              # Exploratory notebooks{% if include_marimo %} (marimo + jupyter){% endif %}

├── tests/                  # Unit tests
├── pyproject.toml          # Python package metadata + deps
├── pixi.toml               # Environment + tasks (reads pyproject.toml)
├── dvc.yaml                # Pipeline definition
└── params.yaml             # Pipeline parameters (datasets, stage configs)
```
